description: Photodynamic therapy may induce an acute stress response mediated by mitogen-activated protein kinase kinase kinase 5 (MAP3K5), its downstream MAPKs that target c-Jun N-terminal kinase (JNK, MAPK8) and p38MAPK, and the transcription factors of the activator protein 1 (AP-1) family.
title: Photodynamic therapy-induced AP-1 survival signaling
